msgctxt "about_whatisthis_title"
msgid "What is <strong>Universalis</strong>?"
msgstr "<strong>Universalis</strong>とは？"

#: 
msgctxt "about_whatisthis_explanation_1"
msgid "The site allows you to view in-game market for multiple servers at anytime, anywhere. It uses crowd-sourced data from multiple sources to provide the most up-to-date prices possible."
msgstr ""

#: 
msgctxt "about_whatisthis_infoquestion"
msgid "What information can I get?"
msgstr "何の情報が取りますか？"

#: 
msgctxt "about_whatisthis_explanation_2"
msgid "All market information is available: Prices, Materia, Retainer, Crafters and even Buyers. Everything that you see in-game is available. Additional data-views have been added such as graphs, extended history and cross-world summary is also included."
msgstr ""

#: 
msgctxt "about_whatisthis_accessquestion"
msgid "Can I have access to the data?"
msgstr ""

#: Don't translate HTML tags.
msgctxt "about_whatisthis_explanation_3"
msgid "<strong>Definitely!</strong>\n"
"<br><br>\n"
"Everything you see on Universalis is open for anyone to use, to learn more about how to access the data using a REST API Service, check out the %s documentation."
msgstr "<strong>もちろんです！</strong>\n"
"<br><br>\n"
"todo"

